additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 13 11 26 or for New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. Pressurised dispenser. Extremely flammable. Keep in a cool place out of the sun. Do not store in sunlight.
